window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He will do anything to keep her… even kill.</b></p> <p>I came to Dublin to fix my relationship with my brother. I didn't mean to become obsessed with the tattooed goddess with haunted eyes—his best friend.</p> <p>One lie turned into another. Stalking her turned into taking her. Now, I'll do anything to keep her… including putting my baby in her belly. Even if it means I lose my brother forever.</p> <p>But her dangerous past is returning to claim her. If my brother and I can't put aside our hate, she's worse than dead.</p> <p><i>If you like morally grey stalker book boyfriends with serious touch-her-and-die vibes, then you'll devour </i>Devilish Ink. Devilish Ink <i>is a full-length standalone with a HEA. This book includes obsessive/possessive behaviour and other dark matters. A complete list of content warnings can be found on the author's website.</i></p>"; 
